      "writtenOn": "2026-04-02T10:33:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "do we need both the `go func` and enqueue? i.e. could we not do the sleep inside the enqueue?\n\nI\u0027m also curious how gopls implements this, to see if it\u0027s a different or better approach.",
      "revId": "ab163d2ebf564aaa82d7ab59fc3d009a76494e27",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
